        "message": {
          "id": "msg_perf_2",
          "author": {"role": "assistant"},
          "content": {"content_type": "text", "parts": ["First: EXPLAIN ANALYZE the query. Common wins:\n\n1. Missing indexes on WHERE/JOIN columns\n2. N+1 query problem\n3. SELECT * instead of needed columns\n4. No query limits\n5. Aggregation without GROUP BY optimization\n\nWith 10M rows, indexes are critical. What's your current schema?"]},
